@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "MD's Greeting";
}

<style>
    /* ── HERO SECTION ── */
    .cp-hero {
        position: relative;
        width: 100vw;
        margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%);
        height: 380px;
        overflow: hidden;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-end;
        padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .cp-hero-bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
       background: url('/images/ceo.jpg') center 20% / cover no-repeat;
        filter: brightness(0.85);
        transform: scale(1.03);
        transition: transform 8s ease;
    }

    .cp-hero:hover .cp-hero-bg {
        transform: scale(1.0);
    }

    .cp-hero-overlay {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(10,20,50,0.2) 0%, rgba(10,20,50,0.75) 100%);
    }

    .cp-hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        max-width: 1140px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .cp-breadcrumb {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #60a5fa;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .cp-hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #ffffff;
        letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* ── CONTENT WRAPPER ── */
    .cp-content-wrapper {
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0;
        margin-top: -2rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 3;
        box-shadow: 0 -4px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        padding: 3rem 2rem 4rem;
        max-width: 1140px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        width: 100%;
    }

    /* ── GREETING LAYOUT ── */
    .greet-layout {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
        gap: 3rem;
        align-items: start;
    }

    /* ── LEFT: PHOTO + NAME CARD ── */
    .greet-photo-col {
        position: sticky;
        top: 2rem;
    }

    .greet-photo-wrap {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 14px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
        border: 3px solid #dc2626;
    }

        .greet-photo-wrap img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 360px;
            object-fit: cover;
            object-position: top center;
            display: block;
        }

    .greet-name-plate {
        background: #1e293b;
        border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
        padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
        text-align: center;
    }

        .greet-name-plate .gn-name {
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        .greet-name-plate .gn-title-line {
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #60a5fa;
        }

    /* ── ASSOCIATION LOGOS ── */
    .assoc-logos {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 1.25rem;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .assoc-logo-item {
        background: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 0.6rem 0.75rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
        flex: 1 1 80px;
        max-width: 100px;
    }

        .assoc-logo-item:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(37,99,235,0.12);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .assoc-logo-item img {
            width: 52px;
            height: 52px;
            object-fit: contain;
            display: block;
        }

        .assoc-logo-item span {
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.8px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #475569;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

    /* ── RIGHT: GREETING TEXT ── */
    .greet-text-col {
    }

    .greet-label {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1.5px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #dc2626;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .greet-heading {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .greet-divider {
        width: 50px;
        height: 4px;
        background: #dc2626;
        border-radius: 2px;
        margin: 1rem 0 1.75rem;
    }
    }

    .greet-salutation {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .greet-para {
        font-size: 0.935rem;
        color: #4b5563;
        line-height: 1.9;
        margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
    }

    .greet-sign-block {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        padding-top: 1.5rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .greet-sign-name {
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1e293b;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .greet-sign-post {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #dc2626;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .greet-sign-honours {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #6b7280;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @@media (max-width: 860px) {
        .greet-layout {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .greet-photo-col {
            position: static;
        }

        .greet-photo-wrap img {
            height: 300px;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 600px) {
        .cp-hero {
            height: 260px;
        }

        .cp-content-wrapper {
            padding: 2rem 1.25rem 3rem;
        }

        .greet-heading {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
    }
</style>

<!-- ── HERO ── -->
<div class="cp-hero">
    <div class="cp-hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="cp-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="cp-hero-content">
        <p class="cp-breadcrumb">About Us / MD's Greeting</p>
        <h1 class="cp-hero-title">Managing Director's Greeting</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- ── MAIN CONTENT ── -->
<div class="cp-content-wrapper">
    <div class="greet-layout">

        <!-- LEFT COLUMN: Photo + Name Plate + Logos -->
        <div class="greet-photo-col">
            <div class="greet-photo-wrap">
                <img src="/images/Dato-Dr-Roslan-Ahmad.jpg" alt="Dato' Dr. Roslan Ahmad" />
                <div class="greet-name-plate">
                    <p class="gn-name">Dato' Dr. Roslan Ahmad</p>
                    <p class="gn-title-line">Managing Director</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Association Logos -->
            <div class="assoc-logos">
                <div class="assoc-logo-item">
                    <img src="/images/license/iamsp.png" alt="IAMSP Logo" />
                    <span>IAMSP</span>
                </div>
                <div class="assoc-logo-item">
                    <img src="/images/license/mosva.jpg" alt="MOSVA Logo" />
                    <span>MOSVA</span>
                </div>
                <div class="assoc-logo-item">
                    <img src="/images/license/mastra.png" alt="MASTRA Logo" />
                    <span>MASTRA</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- RIGHT COLUMN: Greeting Text -->
        <div class="greet-text-col">
            <p class="greet-label">Message from Leadership</p>
            <h2 class="greet-heading">YBHG DATO' ROSLAN BIN AHMAD</h2>
            <div class="greet-divider"></div>

            <p class="greet-salutation">Managing Director's Greetings</p>

            <p class="greet-para">
                My sincerest gratitude to everyone visiting SYNERGY MARINE (M) SDN. BHD. (SMMSB)'s official website.
            </p>

            <p class="greet-para">
                As a true-blue Malaysian setup company, it has set its foothold in the market from humble beginnings.
                Every facet of the company has been structured and perfected through sheer experience, productive and
                progressive mindsets. Setting the pace with the culture striving for excellence, perfection, high
                working performance and client satisfaction, SMMSB continue its mission with the same drive and
                ambition that has established SMMSB as a force to be reckoned with.
            </p>

            <p class="greet-para">
                Since our establishment in 2012, we have been exerting our utmost efforts under our customer
                satisfaction and excellent services ideology. I am happy to note that SMMSB has further been able to
                contribute to the sustainable growth and development of its business objective in Oil &amp; Gas
                Industries in the segment of OSV (Offshore Support Vessel) chartering challenge without compromising
                our core values such as 'Care for the Environment', 'Occupational Health &amp; Safety', and
                Equality &amp; Quality.
            </p>

            <p class="greet-para">
                Sustaining and continuously growing in these challenging years. Towards 2023, four key focus areas:
                addressing market liquidity; addressing fair and sustainable contracting mechanisms; promoting local
                industry participation and international expansion; advocating for the energy transition and
                transformation — we hope to continue our efforts to improve the industry. With the strategic
                direction previously set.
            </p>

            <p class="greet-para">
                We are optimistic that our performance will continue to be strong over the next few years, and we
                believe the outlook for the oil and gas industry is bright, given the significant improvement in
                our backlog.
            </p>

            <p class="greet-para">
                I would like to acknowledge and express my deepest appreciation to personnel of SMMSB and associates
                for their generous and magnificent support and contributions to this business journey, which has
                inspired, touched and illuminated myself through their presence. So let us continue to address the
                issues facing our industry and work together to prepare it for a brighter and more sustainable future.
            </p>

            <p class="greet-para" style="font-style: italic; color: #374151;">Thank you.</p>

            <div class="greet-sign-block">
                <p class="greet-sign-name">YBHG. DATO' ROSLAN BIN AHMAD</p>
                <p class="greet-sign-post">Managing Director</p>
                <p class="greet-sign-honours">DIMP, DKSD, PJK.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>
